      <title>德国最高法院拒绝试图停止债务刹车投票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-14/germany-s-top-court-rejects-attempt-to-stop-debt-brake-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国最高法院驳回了紧急竞标，以防止该国即将离任的议会对宪法进行更改，以消除国防借贷的限制，并建立了5000亿欧元（5440亿美元）的基础设施基金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-14/germany-s-top-court-rejects-attempt-to-stop-debt-brake-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 14 Mar 2025 15:07:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>华盛顿特区，国会“毁灭性”削减的地区牙套</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-14/washington-dc-virginia-and-maryland-brace-for-cuts-to-schools-transit-police</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当地领导人＆nbsp;正在提高有关国会一项停车措施的警报，该措施将触发城市的预算短缺10亿美元，并影响更广泛的弗吉尼亚州和马里兰州地区。&gt; ]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-14/washington-dc-virginia-and-maryland-brace-for-cuts-to-schools-transit-police</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 14 Mar 2025 15:02:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>菲律宾的杜特尔特被捕后首次面对刑事法院</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-14/philippines-duterte-faces-criminal-court-for-first-time-after-arrest</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾前总统罗德里戈·杜特尔特（Rodrigo Duterte）周五在国际刑事法院出庭，自涉嫌在致命毒品战争中犯下的人类犯罪而被捕以来。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-14/philippines-duterte-faces-criminal-court-for-first-time-after-arrest</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 14 Mar 2025 14:16:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普要求俄罗斯在停火推动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-14/trump-asks-russia-to-spare-lives-of-surrounded-ukraine-troops</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普总统呼吁俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京（Vladimir Putin）挽救成千上万的乌克兰军队的生命，他说处于“非常糟糕和脆弱的地位”，避免他说的是自第二次世界大战以来与任何事物不同的屠杀。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-14/trump-asks-russia-to-spare-lives-of-surrounded-ukraine-troops</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 14 Mar 2025 13:44:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>梅尔斯（Merz</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-14/merz-reaches-agreement-with-greens-on-german-spending-package</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国保守党领导人弗里德里希·梅尔斯（Friedrich Merz）就债务资助的国防和基础设施的支出方案达成了一项协议，在下周在议会举行的紧缩投票之前克服了一个关键障碍。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-14/merz-reaches-agreement-with-greens-on-german-spending-package</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 14 Mar 2025 12:43:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈马斯提出释放以色列被驳回为破坏的美国人质</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-14/hamas-says-it-agreed-to-release-us-israeli-hostage-four-bodies</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哈马斯说，它愿意释放所有美国以色列人质，其中包括一个活着的人，以色列被驳回，以示意播种该国与华盛顿之间的不和谐。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-14/hamas-says-it-agreed-to-release-us-israeli-hostage-four-bodies</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 14 Mar 2025 11:26:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
