    <item>
      <title>我们在寻求停火时悄悄地收紧俄罗斯制裁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-13/us-quietly-tightens-russia-sanctions-as-it-seeks-ceasefire-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国正在通过限制能源付款来收紧对俄罗斯的制裁，即使它与总统弗拉基米尔·普京（Vladimir Putin）就乌克兰战争进行了和平谈判。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-13/us-quietly-tightens-russia-sanctions-as-it-seeks-ceasefire-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Mar 2025 22:50:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>舒默（Schumer）撤退了关闭威胁，增强了比尔的前景</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-13/schumer-signals-he-won-t-block-gop-bill-to-avert-shutdown</link>
      <description><![CDATA[参议院民主党领导人查克·舒默（Chuck Schumer）有两种选择，因为时钟到政府资助截止日期：放弃他的威胁以阻止共和党法案或迫使3月15日的破坏性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-13/schumer-signals-he-won-t-block-gop-bill-to-avert-shutdown</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Mar 2025 22:30:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>挪威通过欧盟法律以赢得关税的豁免</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-12/norway-steps-up-bid-to-pass-eu-laws-to-win-tariffs-exemption</link>
      <description><![CDATA[挪威正在努力说服欧盟免除任何广泛的保护性关税，以便在唐纳德·特朗普总统在金属上与税款发动贸易战后对美国的回应。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-12/norway-steps-up-bid-to-pass-eu-laws-to-win-tariffs-exemption</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Mar 2025 09:00:31 GMT</pubDate>
